<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="63" type="redescription">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Redescription.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="63">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Female.</emphasis>
Length of body 2.93 mm (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figure 5. Aphidius areolatus Ashmead, female A body B wing C antennae D head E propodeum F dorsal view of petiole G lateral view of petiole." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.86.70767.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/601089" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">5A</figureCitation>
). Length of fore wing 2.63 mm (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figure 5. Aphidius areolatus Ashmead, female A body B wing C antennae D head E propodeum F dorsal view of petiole G lateral view of petiole." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.86.70767.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/601089" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">5B</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
